OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBen Wallace slaps down     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fminister in army cash row  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Defence Secretary Ben Wallace has      
OL,6, dismissed criticism from veterans'     
OL,7, minister Johnny Mercer of his efforts  
OL,8, to secure more armed forces funding.   
OL,10,FContrasting their responsibilities, he 
OL,11,Fsaid Mr Mercer was a "junior minister" 
OL,12,Fwho "doesn't have to run the budget".  
OL,14,FMr Mercer has claimed it is "not       
OL,15,Fcredible" for Mr Wallace to say the UK 
OL,16,Fmilitary has been "hollowed out".      
OL,18,FHis wife, Felicity Cornelius-Mercer,   
OL,19,Faccused the defence secretary of       
OL,20,Ftreating her husband with "disdain".   
